payment
=========

Payment Sources : 
    - Wallet 
    - Saving Acc
    - Pay Later (Borrow) 
    - Co branded credit card
    
Payment Methods :
    - UPI
    - CC/Db
    - NB
    - IMPS/NEFT/RTGS
    - Cheque
    - ATM Withdrawl

Payment Types:
    - P2P transfer
    - Self Transfer
    - Merchant Payment
    - Merchant collect request
    - Repayment (Borrow)
    - Platform fee (Audo debit)
    - Subscription/ Mandates(recurring)
    
Payment Status: 
    - Pending
    - Success
    - Failure
    - Reversed
    - Refunded
    
